dataset.title: Land Use 2014 WGS84
dataset.description:
Primary Land Use per Parcel for Cuyahoga County, Ohio
It consists of areas of land use as recorded by the Cuyahoga County Fiscal Officer.
  • Land Use By Type: areas grouped and symbolized by land use type
Created in 2014.

dataset.title: Combined Parcels - Non-Cleveland Only
dataset.description: Survey Parcels with CAMA Real Property characteristics within Cuyahoga County.  Point parcels have been converted to polygons and appended, along with the air parcel polygons, for a single parcel featureclass.  This layer only contains parcels with a listed city that is not Cleveland. LAST UPDATED JULY 2020.

dataset.title: Combined Parcels - Cleveland Only
dataset.description: Survey Parcels with CAMA Real Property characteristics.  Point parcels have been converted to polygons and appended, along with the air parcel polygons, for a single parcel featureclass.  The layer only contains parcels with a listed city of Cleveland. LAST UPDATED JULY 2020.
